  • Method Details

    • of

      public static HttpResponseStatus of(int statusCode, String reasonPhrase)
      Returns an HttpResponseStatus for the specified statusCode and reasonPhrase. Generally, the constants in HttpResponseStatus should be used.
      Parameters:
      statusCode - the three digit status-code indicating status of the response
      reasonPhrase - the reason-phrase portion of the response
      Returns:
      an HttpResponseStatus
